{"tid":1259774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬漢6‧16天星碼頭遭推跌亡　警拘一青年","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:18:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6df72a03db5a5d49b35c1cbe9a8385fdb60877ff","tid":1259774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190626/s00001/cbdc464eae3b43de89f5d92bbba766bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190626%2Fs00001%2Fcbdc464eae3b43de89f5d92bbba766bd.jpg&h=5959f877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣6月16日發起反《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，當晚10時許，一名六旬男子被發現倒臥在中環天星碼頭對出，送往瑪麗醫院治理，兩日後不治。驗屍報告顯示，他的後腦有一度13厘米裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，事主當晚曾與另一名男子因排隊上船發生糾紛，被人推倒在地上，後腦着地。警方今日（26日）在屯門區拘捕一名26歲男子，涉嫌謀殺，初步有人承認與案有關。港島總區重案組總督察冼國明稱，二人不相識，事件不涉武器。<br />\n<br />\n警方消息指出，該六旬男子當日到太古廣場，悼念前一晚在該商場高處墮下的男子，而26歲男子則剛完成民陣的遊行，二人當時正排隊準備乘船過海。"},{"pid":"97aa22b2bd0adf8019a731876822bd9826afceaf","tid":1259774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190626/s00001/1561556693198/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190626%2Fs00001%2F1561556693198%2F&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=65520ae6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190626%2Fs00001%2F1561556693198%2F&h=b8cd7501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190626/s00001/1561556693198/</a>"},{"pid":"b14aa76e9efc46eefc703a592ccb85f6d9b4e8a7","tid":1259774,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d6f3f7983a7f0fc362bf6b23e76894fb8aae5bd","tid":1259774,"uid":13731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:23:05.000Z